      "description": "$19,800 - Honest fair-condition vehicle that presents as a usable, older car with visible wear consistent with age. Expect cosmetic imperfections, some signs of use inside and out, and a generally average overall appearance rather than a standout, showroom-level example. The body and interior are serviceable, but buyers should come expecting normal aging, blemishes, and the kind of wear you would expect from a vehicle in this category. A reasonable choice for someone seeking practical transportation at a more affordable price point, as long as expectations are kept realistic.",
